Package: aba
Title: Automated biomarker analysis in R
Version: 0.0.9
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nicholas",
           family = "Cullen",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nickcullen31@gmail.com")
Description: Automated biomarker analysis in R (abaR) is intended to make it
    easier to fit statistical models on biomarker data, to make it easier to
    use biomarkers to plan and analysis clinical trials, and to facilitate more
    multi-cohort validation studies.
